On an individual basis when more information is available, such as type of previous Caesarean delivery, other factors are taken into account and women with two previous Caesarean deliveries may be considered for VBAC. [Ref: Society of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists of Canada. Guidelines for vaginal birth after previous caesarean birth. SOGC clinical practice guidelines. Number 155, February 2005.
